2020-08-20T23:25:44.000Z","msg":"有咩好驚 俾人盜用咪盜用 打上card centre講返 過1-2日寄過張俾你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T01:50:17.000Z","msg":"你都幾豁達架喎<br />\n即係我d 錢擺咗喺銀行，就預咗俾人偷咁呀？<br />\n只要我同返銀行proof 唔係我攞同用，就冇事喇？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個概念有 d 問題...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"咁事實真係同銀行講返就無事 同埋人地想偷既話都無計 你save card係Device都隨時俾人偷"},{"pid":"053c9f9a5df3bf848f7f6b8213fea164c0b801e3","tid":2151080,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"聽過有人會抄底曬料<br />\n然後用TOR BROWSER 外國買野<br />\n最後碌左人地十幾萬全身而退"},{"pid":"3ed9216d4d7e282bbb1eaeb302caccef7b57cfc9","tid":2151080,"uid":41238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b762a7f4eb926936962254e85b5630d7868de40","tid":2151080,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82ba24737b87784b1bb79ecf0075407f110c721","tid":2151080,"uid":41238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"097d95c997752740cc2b4eee3832fc7d1526b005","tid":2151080,"uid":248116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"例如我Eaton個例子<br />\n房錢碌一次<br />\n按金碌多次<br />\n最後就問我可唔可以撕貼紙睇number<br />\n而家新卡例如CITI /Enjoy卡所有號碼印晒後面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"邊度間間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把酒店全程都唔洗出示信用卡<br />\n我做嘢間五星，連deposit 都唔收<br />\n啲客走數都唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"咁即係你個間檔做野有問題囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話走數都唔Care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea86443e3219c1156bc1fbac9b32837ebc2b9225","tid":2151080,"uid":181639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"絕大部分酒店，本地品牌又好，Marriott, Hyatt, Hilton, Accor, IHG, Four Seasons之類嘅國際集團都好，除咗房費個amount之外都一定會要求客人留低security deposit (佢地會叫incidentals deposit)，你可以比用現金或者信用卡等留。金額太概每晚幾百至一千。哩個喺一個commom practice，全球嘅酒店，尤其是連鎖集團會check得好緊。<br />\n<br />\n如果用信用卡，佢地喺一定會抄低你嘅card no同exp date （今時今日多數入電腦），但多數唔需要後面果3個字number。通常會喺check in直接碌卡，唔會charge，但會frozen咗個credit （佢地叫做pre-authorization) 去擔保你嘅damage (if any)或者spa, laundry, dining等嘅消費，因為驚你走數。Check-out先會喺pre-authorized credit入面過返最後個實數。<br />\n<br />\n如果你經Expedia/<a href=\"http://Booking.com/Agoda哩啲OTAs訂房預先比咗錢，好多時酒店喺唔會有你嘅card\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBooking.com%2FAgoda%E5%93%A9%E5%95%B2OTAs%E8%A8%82%E6%88%BF%E9%A0%90%E5%85%88%E6%AF%94%E5%92%97%E9%8C%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%9A%E6%99%82%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%96%BA%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%A0%E5%98%85card&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=7444f109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Booking.com/Agoda哩啲OTAs訂房預先比咗錢，好多時酒店喺唔會有你嘅card</a> details，因謂個payment喺直接去OTAs，所以你check in果陣會問你拎多次張卡碌。<br />\n<br />\n如果你喺經官網訂，或者喺OTAs揀咗到酒店比錢，佢地會有你card details，但都喺會喺check in果陣去拎多次張卡對名，因為要avoid fraud case。<br />\n<br />\n如果你對哩樣嘢有concern，你可以比cash跟住check out退返，或者要求酒店先同你settle房租再close咗你個folio，你有spending就即場比錢（唔可以掛落房）。"},{"pid":"aa4b3b801e3988a80b26e82f24ead9cd3b738028","tid":2151080,"uid":181639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ed9216d4d7e282bbb1eaeb302caccef7b57cfc9","tid":2151080,"uid":41238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b762a7f4eb926936962254e85b5630d7868de40","tid":2151080,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82ba24737b87784b1bb79ecf0075407f110c721","tid":2151080,"uid":41238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"邊度間間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把酒店全程都唔洗出示信用卡<br />\n我做嘢間五星，連deposit 都唔收<br />\n啲客走數都唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so